high_descs: Turn and go to the table.
Pick up a potato on the table.
Turn and go to the refrigerator.
Chill the potato in the refrigerator.
Turn around and go to the table.
Put the potato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled potato on the table.

high_descs: Turn right then make steps face the table on your left
Pick up the potato on the table
Turn left then head to the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the potato then close the fridge
Turn left and walk towards the table on you left
Put the potato on the table beside the tomato
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled potato on the table

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward, then turn right and begin walking across the room, hang a left and walk up to the white table.
Pick up the sweet potato that is closest to the white mug on the white table.
Walk over to the fridge that is behind you.
Open the fridge and put the sweet potato in the fridge then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge and take out the now chilled sweet potato then close the door.
Walk back over to the white table that is behind you against the wall.
Put the chilled sweet potato on the white table to the right of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled sweet potato on a white table.
